Package: greta.gam
Type: Package
Title: Generalised Additive Models in greta using mgcv
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Nick", "Golding", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                 email = "nick.golding.research@gmail.com"),
          person("David", "L", "Miller", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                 email = "dave@ninepointeightone.net"), 
Maintainer: Nick Golding <nick.golding.research@gmail.com>
Description: A module for greta that lets you use mgcv's smoother functions 
    and formula syntax to define smooth terms for use in a greta model. You 
    can then define your own likelihood to complete the model, and fit it by 
    MCMC. 
License: GPL(>=2) 
Imports: mgcv
Depends: greta
Suggests: testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
